{
  "name": "Paper Bomb Barrage",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Bukijutsu.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You prepare a cluster of paper bombs which are consumed in the casting of this jutsu, in between your fingers on both hands and launch them at a single Target covering them in the prepared Bombs.</p><p>A target you can see within range, makes a Dexterity saving throw, taking 7d4 Fire Damage on a failed save or half as much on a successful one.</p><p>Creatures within 10ft of the target creature, excluding the target  creature, also make the Dexterity Save, taking 5d4 Fire damage on a failed save or half as much on a successful one.</p><p>For every quality of item used above the basic item quality, you increase this jutsu's damage by 4d4.  </p>",
